title: Race Script
content:
ReplicatedStorage = game:GetService("ReplicatedStorage")
ServerStorage = game:GetService("ServerStorage")
Players = game:GetService("Players")

RaceSystem = ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild("RaceSystem")
RaceGui = RaceSystem:WaitForChild("RaceGui")
WinGui = RaceSystem:WaitForChild("WinGui")

TeleportPlayerRemoteEvent = ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild("Remotes").Races.TeleportPlayer
DismissRemoteEvent = ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild("Remotes").Races.DismissRace

StartRaceBindableEvent = ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild("Bindables").StartRace
FinishRaceBindableEvent = ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild("Bindables").FinishRace

RaceFolder = ServerStorage:WaitForChild("Race")
RaceMaps = RaceFolder:GetChildren()

RacesConfig = require(ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild("Configs"):WaitForChild("Races"))

ChosenMap = nil

GuiShown = false
GuiClones = {}

NotDecided = {}
FinishedPlayers = {}

function SpawnGui()
	for _, Player in pairs(Players:GetPlayers()) do
		local GuiClone = RaceGui:Clone()
		GuiClone.Parent = Player.PlayerGui
		table.insert(GuiClones, GuiClone)
		table.insert(NotDecided, Player)
	end
end

function SpawnWinnerGui()
	for _, Player in pairs(Players:GetPlayers()) do
		local GuiClone = WinGui:Clone()

		if #FinishedPlayers >= 3 then
			GuiClone.Frame.First.Image = Players:GetUserThumbnailAsync(FinishedPlayers[1].UserId, Enum.ThumbnailType.AvatarBust, Enum.ThumbnailSize.Size420x420)
			GuiClone.Frame.Second.Image = Players:GetUserThumbnailAsync(FinishedPlayers[2].UserId, Enum.ThumbnailType.AvatarBust, Enum.ThumbnailSize.Size420x420)
			GuiClone.Frame.Third.Image = Players:GetUserThumbnailAsync(FinishedPlayers[3].UserId, Enum.ThumbnailType.AvatarBust, Enum.ThumbnailSize.Size420x420)
		elseif #FinishedPlayers == 2 then
			GuiClone.Frame.First.Image = Players:GetUserThumbnailAsync(FinishedPlayers[1].UserId, Enum.ThumbnailType.AvatarBust, Enum.ThumbnailSize.Size420x420)
			GuiClone.Frame.Second.Image = Players:GetUserThumbnailAsync(FinishedPlayers[2].UserId, Enum.ThumbnailType.AvatarBust, Enum.ThumbnailSize.Size420x420)
			GuiClone.Frame.Third:Destroy()
		elseif #FinishedPlayers == 1 then
			GuiClone.Frame.First.Image = Players:GetUserThumbnailAsync(FinishedPlayers[1].UserId, Enum.ThumbnailType.AvatarBust, Enum.ThumbnailSize.Size420x420)
			GuiClone.Frame.Second:Destroy()
			GuiClone.Frame.Third:Destroy()
		end

		GuiClone.Parent = Player.PlayerGui

		if #FinishedPlayers == 0 then
			GuiClone:Destroy()
		end
	end
end

function DestroyGui(RemoveAll: boolean)
	if RemoveAll == false then
		for i, v in pairs(NotDecided) do
			local Index = table.find(GuiClones, v.PlayerGui.RaceGui)
			if Index then
				table.remove(NotDecided, table.find(NotDecided, v))
				table.remove(GuiClones, Index)
				v.PlayerGui.RaceGui:Destroy()
			end
		end

		for i, v in pairs(GuiClones) do
			v.Background.Header.Text = "Race Ending In"
		end
	else
		for i, v in pairs(GuiClones) do
			v:Destroy()
		end

		GuiClones = {}
	end
end

function DestroyWinGui()
	for _, Player in pairs(Players:GetPlayers()) do
		if Player.PlayerGui:FindFirstChild("WinGui") then
			Player.PlayerGui.WinGui:Destroy()
		end
	end
end

function UpdateGuiTimer(RaceInProgress: boolean)
	if RaceInProgress == false then
		for i, v in ipairs(GuiClones) do
			if v:FindFirstChild("Background") then
				v.Background.Timer.Text = string.format("%02i:%02i", RacesConfig.Timer / 60, RacesConfig.Timer % 60)
			end
		end
	else
		for i, v in ipairs(GuiClones) do
			if v:FindFirstChild("Background") then
				v.Background.Timer.Text = string.format("%02i:%02i", RacesConfig.InProgressTimer / 60, RacesConfig.InProgressTimer % 60)
			end
		end
	end
end

function StartRace()
	FinishedPlayers = {}
	NotDecided = {}
	GuiShown = false
	ChosenMap.Wall.CanCollide = true

	local StartTimer = coroutine.create(RacesConfig.StartTimer)
	coroutine.resume(StartTimer)
end

TeleportPlayerRemoteEvent.OnServerEvent:Connect(function(Player)
	if Player.Character then
		local HumanoidRootPart = Player.Character:FindFirstChild("HumanoidRootPart")
		if HumanoidRootPart then
			local Spawns = ChosenMap.SpawnParts:GetChildren()
			local Index = math.random(1, #Spawns)
			HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = Spawns[Index].CFrame + Vector3.new(0, 2, 0)

			local TableIndex = table.find(NotDecided, Player)
			if TableIndex then
				table.remove(NotDecided, TableIndex)
			end
		end
	end
end)

DismissRemoteEvent.OnServerEvent:Connect(function(Player, GUI)
	local Index = table.find(GuiClones, GUI)
	if Index then
		table.remove(NotDecided, table.find(NotDecided, Player))
		table.remove(GuiClones, Index)
		GUI:Destroy()
	end
end)

StartRaceBindableEvent.Event:Connect(function()
	DestroyGui(false)

	local RaceInProgress = coroutine.create(RacesConfig.RaceInProgress)
	coroutine.resume(RaceInProgress)

	local Wall = ChosenMap:WaitForChild("Wall")
	Wall.CanCollide = false
end)

FinishRaceBindableEvent.Event:Connect(function()
	DestroyGui(true)

	ChosenMap.Parent = ServerStorage.Race

	SpawnWinnerGui()

	if #FinishedPlayers >= 3 then
		FinishedPlayers[1]:WaitForChild("leaderstats"):WaitForChild("Rings").Value += 5000
		FinishedPlayers[2]:WaitForChild("leaderstats"):WaitForChild("Rings").Value += 2500
		FinishedPlayers[3]:WaitForChild("leaderstats"):WaitForChild("Rings").Value += 1000
	elseif #FinishedPlayers == 2 then
		FinishedPlayers[1]:WaitForChild("leaderstats"):WaitForChild("Rings").Value += 5000
		FinishedPlayers[2]:WaitForChild("leaderstats"):WaitForChild("Rings").Value += 2500
	elseif #FinishedPlayers == 1 then
		FinishedPlayers[1]:WaitForChild("leaderstats"):WaitForChild("Rings").Value += 5000
	end

	local Intermission = coroutine.create(RacesConfig.Intermission)
	coroutine.resume(Intermission)
end)

function RandomMap()
	local ChosenMapIndex = math.random(1, #RaceMaps)
	RaceMaps[ChosenMapIndex].Parent = workspace
	ChosenMap = RaceMaps[ChosenMapIndex]
end

function LoadFirstRace()
	RandomMap()
	StartRace()
end

LoadFirstRace()

while task.wait(1) do
	if RacesConfig.Timer > 0 then
		if #ServerStorage.Race:GetChildren() == #RaceMaps then
			RandomMap()
		end
		if GuiShown == false then
			GuiShown = true
			SpawnGui()
		end

		UpdateGuiTimer(false)
	else 
		UpdateGuiTimer(true)
		
		ChosenMap.FinishArea.Touched:Connect(function(OtherPart: BasePart)
			if OtherPart.Parent then
				local Player = Players:GetPlayerFromCharacter(OtherPart.Parent)
				if Player then
					if table.find(FinishedPlayers, Player) then
						return
					end

					table.insert(FinishedPlayers, Player)

					if Player.Character then
						local HumanoidRootPart = Player.Character:FindFirstChild("HumanoidRootPart")
						if HumanoidRootPart then
							local Spawns = workspace.Spawns:GetChildren()
							local Index = math.random(1, #Spawns)
							HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = Spawns[Index].CFrame + Vector3.new(0, 2, 0)
						end
					end
				end
			end
		end)
	end

	if RacesConfig.Timer <= 0 and RacesConfig.InProgressTimer <= 0 then
		task.wait(5)
		DestroyWinGui()

		if RacesConfig.IntermissionTimer <= 0 then
			StartRace()
		end
	end
end

title: Race Config
content:
local ReplicatedStorage = game:GetService("ReplicatedStorage")

local BindablesFolder = ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild("Bindables")

local Races = {
	Timer = 0,               
	InProgressTimer = 0,      
	IntermissionTimer = 0,    
	
	InitialCountdownDuration = 30,
	RaceDuration = 60,
	IntermissionDuration = 30,
	
	CurrentPhase = "None"     
}

function Races.StartTimer()
	if Races.CurrentPhase ~= "None" and Races.CurrentPhase ~= "IntermissionComplete" then
		return
	end
	
	Races.CurrentPhase = "Countdown"
	Races.Timer = Races.InitialCountdownDuration

	while Races.Timer > 0 and Races.CurrentPhase == "Countdown" do
		task.wait(1)
		Races.Timer -= 1
	end

	if Races.Timer == 0 and Races.CurrentPhase == "Countdown" then 
		Races.CurrentPhase = "CountdownComplete"
		local StartRaceBindableEvent = BindablesFolder:WaitForChild("StartRace")
		StartRaceBindableEvent:Fire()
	end
end

function Races.RaceInProgress()
	if Races.CurrentPhase ~= "CountdownComplete" then
		return
	end
	
	Races.CurrentPhase = "InProgress"
	Races.InProgressTimer = Races.RaceDuration

	while Races.InProgressTimer > 0 and Races.CurrentPhase == "InProgress" do
		task.wait(1)
		Races.InProgressTimer -= 1
	end

	if Races.InProgressTimer == 0 and Races.CurrentPhase == "InProgress" then
		Races.CurrentPhase = "InProgressComplete"
		local FinishRaceBindableEvent = BindablesFolder:WaitForChild("FinishRace")
		FinishRaceBindableEvent:Fire() 
	end
end

function Races.Intermission()
	if Races.CurrentPhase ~= "InProgressComplete" then
		return
	end
	
	Races.CurrentPhase = "Intermission"
	Races.IntermissionTimer = Races.IntermissionDuration

	while Races.IntermissionTimer > 0 and Races.CurrentPhase == "Intermission" do
		task.wait(1)
		Races.IntermissionTimer -= 1
	end

	if Races.IntermissionTimer == 0 and Races.CurrentPhase == "Intermission" then
		Races.CurrentPhase = "IntermissionComplete"
	end
end

function Races.GetState()
	return {
		Phase = Races.CurrentPhase,
		TimeRemaining = Races.Timer, 
		CountdownTimer = Races.Timer,
		InProgressTimer = Races.InProgressTimer,
		IntermissionTimer = Races.IntermissionTimer,
		InitialCountdownDuration = Races.InitialCountdownDuration,
		RaceDuration = Races.RaceDuration,
		IntermissionDuration = Races.IntermissionDuration
	}
end

function Races.ResetSystem()
    Races.CurrentPhase = "None"
    Races.Timer = 0
    Races.InProgressTimer = 0
    Races.IntermissionTimer = 0

end

return Races
